表的代码预览系统-文件表(OK)

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('sys_file')
and type = 'U')
drop table sys_file
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sys_file */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sys_file (
FileID int identity(1,1),
FileName varchar(500) null,
OldName varchar(500) null,
Size int not null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
constraint PK_SYS_FILE primary key (FileID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('sys_file') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'系统-文件表(OK)',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_file')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'FileID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'FileID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'主键',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'FileID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_file')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'FileName')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'FileName'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'文件名',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'FileName'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_file')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'OldName')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'OldName'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'原文件名',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'OldName'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_file')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'Size')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'Size'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'文件大小',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'Size'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('sys_file')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'AppTime')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'AppTime'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'添加时间',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_file', 'column', 'AppTime'
go
